大数据和Hadoop时代的维度建模和Kimball数据集市

2019-04-24


<span style=”font-size: 13px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 18px;”>

<a href=”https://opendatascience.com/dimensional-modeling-and-kimball-data-marts-in-the-age-of-big-data-and-hadoop/" style=”font-size: 28px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 32px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>大数据和Hadoop时代的维度建模和Kimball数据集市


<span style=”font-size: 28px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>尺寸造型死了吗？

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在我给出这个问题的答案之前，让我们退后一步，首先看一下维度数据建模的含义。

<span style=”font-size: 28px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>为什么我们需要对数据建模？

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>与常见的误解相反，数据模型的唯一目的不是作为设计物理数据库的ER图。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>数据模型表示企业中业务流程的复杂性。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>它们记录了重要的业务规则和概念，有助于标准化关键企业术语。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>它们提供了清晰度，有助于发现有关业务流程的模糊思维和模糊性。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>此外，您可以使用数据模型与其他利益相关者进行通信。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>如果没有蓝图，你就不会建造房屋或桥梁。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>那么为什么要在没有计划的情况下构建数据应用程序（如数据仓库）呢？

<span style=”font-size: 28px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>为什么我们需要尺寸模型？

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>维度建模是一种建模数据的特殊方法。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们还使用单词data mart或star schema作为维度模型的同义词。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>星型模式针对数据分析进行了优化。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>看看下面的维度模型。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>理解起来非常直观。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们立即了解如何按客户，产品或日期对订单数据进行切片和切块，并通过汇总和比较指标来衡量订单业务流程的绩效。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>关于维度建模的核心思想之一是在事务性业务流程中定义最低级别的粒度。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>当我们切片并切块并钻取数据时，这就是我们无法进一步向下钻取的叶级。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>换句话说，星型模式中最低级别的粒度是事实与所有维度表的连接，没有任何聚合。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;”>

<span style=”font-size: 28px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>数据建模与维度建模

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在标准数据建模中，我们的目标是消除数据重复和冗余。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>当数据发生变化时，我们只需要在一个地方进行更改。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这也有助于提高数据质量。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>值不会在多个位置不同步。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>看看下面的模型。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>它包含表示地理概念的各种表。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在规范化模型中，我们为每个实体都有一个单独的表。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在维度模型中，我们只有一个表：地理。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在此表中，城市将重复多次。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>每个城市一次。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>如果国家更改其名称，我们必须在许多地方更新该国家/地区
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;”>
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>注意：标准数据建模也称为3NF建模。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>数据建模的标准方法不适合商业智能工作负载的用途。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>很多表都会产生大量的连接。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>加入缓慢的事情。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在数据分析中，我们尽可能避免使用它们。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在维度模型中，我们将多个相关表格去规范化为一个表格，例如，我们前面示例中的各个表格可以预先连接到一个表格中：地理位置。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>那么为什么有些人声称尺寸建模已经死了呢？

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我认为你会同意一般的数据建模和特别是维度建模是一个非常有用的练习。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>那么为什么有些人声称维度建模在大数据和Hadoop时代没用呢？
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>你可以想象这有很多原因。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>数据仓库已经死了混乱

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>首先，有些人将维度建模与数据仓库混淆。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>他们声称数据仓库已经死亡，因此维度建模也可以归入历史垃圾箱。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这是一个逻辑上连贯的论点。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>但是，数据仓库的概念远未过时。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们始终需要集成且可靠的数据来填充BI仪表板。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>如果您想了解更多信息，我建议我们<a href=”https://sonra.io/big-data-data-warehouse-business-intelligence-professionals/" style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 22px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 87, 50); text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>为数据仓库专业人员提供大数据<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>培训课程 <span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在本课程中，我将详细介绍数据仓库与以往相关的内容。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我还将展示新兴的大数据工具和技术如何对数据仓库有用。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>阅读误解的图式

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我经常听到的第二个论点是这样的。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>“我们遵循读取方法的模式，不再需要对数据进行建模”。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在我看来，读取模式的概念是数据分析中最大的误解之一。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我同意最初将原始数据存储在轻量级模式的数据转储中很有用。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>但是，这个论点不应该被用作不完全建模数据的借口。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>读取方法的模式正在推动下游流程的能力和责任。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>有人仍然需要咬住定义数据类型。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>访问无架构数据转储的每个进程都需要自己弄清楚发生了什么。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这种类型的工作加起来是完全冗余的，并且可以通过定义数据类型和适当的模式来轻松避免。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>重新规范了非规范化。<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>模型的物理方面。

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>实际上是否有一些有效的参数来声明尺寸模型已经过时了？<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>确实有一些比我上面列出的更好的论据。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>他们需要对物理数据建模和Hadoop工作方式有所了解。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>忍受我。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>之前我简要提到了为什么我们在维度上建模数据的原因之一。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这与数据在我们的数据存储中物理存储的方式有关。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在标准数据建模中，每个真实世界实体都有自己的表。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们这样做是为了避免数据冗余以及数据质量问题蔓延到我们的数据中的风险。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们拥有的表越多，我们需要的连接越多。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这是不利的。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>表连接很昂贵，特别是当我们从数据集中连接大量记录时。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>当我们以维度方式对数据建模时，我们将多个表合并为一个。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们说我们预先加入或取消规范化数据。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们现在拥有更少的表，更少的连接，从而降低了延迟并提高了查询性能。
<a href=”https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:6270196381496020992/?commentUrn=urn%3Ali%3Acomment%3A(activity%3A6270196381496020992%2C6270935167486042112)" style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 22px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 87, 50); text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在LinkedIn上<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>参与<a href=”https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:6270196381496020992/?commentUrn=urn%3Ali%3Acomment%3A(activity%3A6270196381496020992%2C6270935167486042112)" style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 22px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 87, 50); text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这篇文章<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>的讨论

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>将去标准化完全结束

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>为什么不将去标准化完全结束呢？<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>摆脱所有联接，只有一个事实表？<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>实际上，这将完全消除对任何连接的需要。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>但是，你可以想象，它有一些副作用。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>首先，它增加了所需的存储量。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们现在需要存储大量冗余数据。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>随着用于数据分析的柱状存储格式的出现，现在这不是一个问题。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>去标准化的一个更大的问题是，每当其中一个属性的值发生变化时，我们就必须在多个位置更新值 - 可能是数千或数百万次更新。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>解决这个问题的一种方法是每晚完全重新加载我们的模型。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>通常，这比应用大量更新要快得多，也更容易。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>列式数据库通常采用以下方法。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>它们首先将更新存储在内存中，然后将它们异步写入磁盘。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>分布式关系数据库（MPP）上的数据分布

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在Hadoop上创建维度模型时，例如Hive，SparkSQL等，我们需要更好地理解该技术的一个核心特征，将其与分布式关系数据库（MPP）（如Teradata等）区分开来。当在MPP中的节点之间分配数据时，我们控制记录的位置。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>基于我们的分区策略，例如散列，列表，范围等，我们可以在同一节点上的列表中共同定位各个记录的键。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>由于我们不需要通过网络发送任何数据，因此保证数据协同定位，我们的连接速度非常快。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>看看下面的例子。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>ORDER和ORDER_ITEM表中具有相同ORDER_ID的记录最终在同一节点上。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;”>
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>order_id和order_item表的键位于相同的节点上。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>Hadoop上的数据分发

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这与基于Hadoop的系统非常不同。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们将数据拆分为大型块，并在Hadoop分布式文件系统（HDFS）上的节点上分发和复制它们。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>有了这种数据分发策略，我们无法保证数据的共存性。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>看看下面的例子。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>ORDER_ID键的记录最终在不同的节点上。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;”>
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>为了加入，我们需要通过网络发送数据，这会影响性能。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>处理此问题的一种策略是跨群集中的所有节点复制其中一个连接表。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这称为广播连接，我们在MPP上使用相同的策略。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>可以想象，它仅适用于小型查找或维度表。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;”>
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>那么当我们拥有一个大型事实表和一个大型维度表（例如客户或产品）时，我们该怎么办？<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>或者当我们有两个大的事实表时。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>Hadoop上的维度模型

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>为了解决这个性能问题，我们可以将大维度表去规范化到事实表中，以保证数据位于同一位置。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们可以在所有节点上广播较小的维度表。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>为了连接两个大的事实表，我们可以使用更高的粒度在表内嵌入具有较低粒度的表，例如嵌套在ORDER表内的大型ORDER_ITEM表。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>现代查询引擎（如Impala或Drill）允许我们平移这些数据
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;”>
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这种嵌套数据的策略对于痛苦的Kimball概念也很有用，例如用于在维模型中表示M：N关系的桥表。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>Hadoop和慢慢改变的维度

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>Hadoop文件系统上的存储是不可变的。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>换句话说，您只能插入和追加记录。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>您无法修改数据。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>如果您来自关系数据仓库背景，这看起来有点奇怪。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>但是，引擎盖下的数据库以类似的方式工作。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在进程异步更新数据文件中的数据之前，它们将所有对数据的更改存储在不可变写入日志中（在Oracle中称为重做日志）。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>不变性对我们的维度模型有什么影响？<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>您可能还记得维度建模过程中慢速变化尺寸（SCD）的概念。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>SCD可选择保留属性更改的历史记录。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>它们允许我们根据某个时间点的属性值报告指标。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>但这不是默认行为。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>默认情况下，我们使用最新值更新维度表。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>那么我们对Hadoop的选择是什么？<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>记得！<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们无法更新数据。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们可以简单地使SCD成为默认行为并审核任何更改。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>如果我们想要针对当前值运行报告，我们可以在仅检索最新值的SCD上创建一个View。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>这可以使用窗口函数轻松完成。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>或者，

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>Hadoop上的存储演变

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>Hadoop平台的供应商并未忽视这些Hadoop限制。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>在Hive中，我们现在有ACID事务和可更新表。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>根据<a href=”https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE/component/12322671/?selectedTab=com.atlassian.jira.jira-projects-plugin:component-issues-panel" style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 700; line-height: 22px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 87, 50); text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>开放主要问题<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>的数量 <span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”> 而且我自己的经验，这个功能似乎还没有生产就绪。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>Cloudera采用了不同的方法。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>使用Kudu，他们创建了一种新的可更新存储格式，它不是HDFS而是本地OS文件系统。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>它完全消除了Hadoop的限制，类似于柱状MPP中的传统存储层。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>一般来说，最好在MPP上运行任何BI和仪表板用例，例如Impala + Kudu，而不是Hadoop。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>已经说过MPP在弹性，并发性和可伸缩性方面都有自己的局限性。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>当您遇到这些限制时，Hadoop及其近亲Spark是BI工作负载的不错选择。

<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>判决。<span style=”font-size: 22px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 900; line-height: 26px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>维度模型和星型模式是否已过时？

<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们都知道Ralph Kimball退休了。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>但他的主要思想和观念仍然有效并且依然存在。<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: inherit;”>我们必须使它们适应新技术和存储类型，但它们仍然可以增加价值。
<span style=”font-size: 14px; font-family: “Open Sans”, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-stretch: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px;”>
